http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Vijayawada/Discontent-brewing-in-Cong.-camp/article13991759.ece

The discontent brewing within the party on the Malladi Vishnu’s arrest came out to the fore at Andhra Ratna Bhavan on Saturday with supporters of the former MLA raising slogans against the senior leaders. During a meeting with party workers, Mr. Vishnu’s supporters accosted the senior leaders and demanded them to take up the issue seriously.They claimed that senior leaders had called on Mr. Vishnu and his family only after the incident. However, a senior leader claimed that they were constantly in touch with the former MLA and his family members and there was no group war in the party.